Property Search and Engaging an Estate Agent: Begin by searching for properties through reputable estate agents or online listings for property for sale in your desired region. Ensure any agent you work with is a registered Agente de la Propiedad Inmobiliaria (API), which signifies a licensed professionalâ€‹
