 to include clauses that protect you (for instance, making the sale conditional on clear title or mortgage approval). From the signing of this contract until completion, neither party can back out without consequence. The agreement will typically allow a period (often 1 to 3 months) before completion, during which the buyer finalizes finances (and, for foreign buyers, the lawyer may use this time to ensure the NIE is obtained, funds are transferred to Spain, and any remaining checks are done)â€‹
